author: Cleo Abram
description:
We’re about to hit 7 million subscribers! We just need ONE MORE…

If we dug a hole through the earth and held onto each other’s feet down it, we’d almost make it ALL THE WAY through to the other side of the earth! We’re assuming we’re all 6 ft tall :)

But we’re not quite there… can you help us reach it? SUBSCRIBE!

#shorts #animation #space #earth  #subscribe
title: I Need 1 More Subscriber!
